their official duties boycott organizer ht smith said of 
miamiarea officials 
under the name boycott miami coalition for progress organizers 
asked groups with national conventions set for the area to go 
somewhere else 
the boycott was announced july 17 as of tuesday the greater 
miami convention and visitors bureau reported eleven groups had 
canceled their gatherings some as far in the future as 1993 
costing nearly 55 million 
other estimates have ranged as high as 12 million 
