past decade from 181000 to 400000 according to interior ministry 
figures more than half are from other western european countries 
government estimates put the number of illegal aliens in spain 
a nation of 40 million at between 70000 and 140000 more than 
half are believed to be moroccan nongovernmental agencies dealing 
with immigrants and refugees say the total number is closer to half 
a million 
spains lightly monitored frontiers its physical proximity to 
