hill amp knowlton coordinated interviews and helped arrange 
national programs and events including national free kuwait day 
national prayer day and the visit of various kuwaitis to the united 
states 
the kuwaiti governmentinexile which is based in taif saudi 
arabia has tried to disseminate information about conditions 
inside kuwait including atrocities reportedly committed by iraqi 
occupation troops 
frank mankiewicz a senior hill amp knowlton executive said the 
