it said the exclusive program linking soliders in bahrain with 
families gathered at designated churches in england and germany 
was being made available to all cable television systems in the 
united states whether or not they are affiliated with visn 
jeffrey c weber programming and operations vice president 
said the hourlong special coproduced with the british 
broadcasting corporation is to be presented by visn at 10 pm est 
christmas eve and will be repeated at 130 pm est on christmas 
day 
the network is owned and operated by the notforprofit national 
interfaith cable coalition made up of 23 roman catholic jewish 
protestant and eastern orthodox faith groups 
 
dayton ohio ap united methodists on the average are older 
and better educated than americans as a whole and a majority of 
them at one time have been affiliated with another denomination a 
survey found 
responses from 758 lay members and 1003 clergy showed 376 
percent of the lay members and 50 percent of the clergy were older 
than 50 compared to 257 percent for the entire country 
for lay members 499 percent had completed at least four years 
of college while 929 percent of the clergy had done so that 
compared to 203 percent of the us population 
 
