the movie event of the year the godfather 
part iii hits the nations screens on christmas day with the 
expectation that francis ford coppola will again prove godfather to 
actors careers 
he did it with the first two sagas of the corleone family 
restoring marlon brando to greatness and establishing al pacino and 
robert de niro as superstars 
the obvious candidate for the bigtime from the new film is andy 
garcia who plays sonny corleones outofwedlock son he has 
already delivered strong supporting performances in the 
untouchables black rain and internal affairs previewers 
of godfather iii seem to agree that garcia has arrived 
there was less agreement about sofia coppola as mary corleone 
the dons daughter when winona ryder was unable to fulfill the 
role coppola made the controversial casting of his own daughter 
her only previous acting came in her fathers films early reaction 
has been fairly negative for sofia some of whose lines had to be 
relooped because of her valley girl voice 
most of the cast are alumni of the previous godfathers 
pacino diane keaton talia shire or established character actors 
