with the opening of the unified market investors will have 
onestop shopping but they will be able to buy and sell only 
through the exchanges 22 member brokerages 
gong haocheng governor of the shanghai branch of chinas 
central bank said buyers are limited to 10 shares apiece of each 
stock issue in order to control speculation bonds are traded only 
for the years 198689 
gong said authorities have not decided whether to let 
foreignfunded enterprises sell shares 
